							<div class="heading-block fancy-title border-bottom-0 title-bottom-border">
								<h4>Why choose <span>Us</span></h4>
							</div>

							<p>Our online book rental system, Books-2-Book, was created keeping our users as the first priority in mind. Being BSc IT students, we know first-hand how stressful the process of finding helpful resources is, as well as how difficult it can be to obtain them. We wished to create a solution that would not only make it easier for students to get the support and resources they need, but also to be able to pay minimal fees.</p>

						</div>

						<div class="col-lg-4">

							<div class="heading-block fancy-title border-bottom-0 title-bottom-border">
								<h4>Our <span>Mission</span></h4>
							</div>

							<p>We believe that no one should be prevented from learning, especially when it comes to finances. We've worked to create a system that provides an affordable way for students to access their course resources while also avoiding the hassle of needing to resell the books. Books are an important tool for education, and it should not be exorbitant to obtain or difficult to access.</p>

						</div>

						<div class="col-lg-4">

							<div class="heading-block fancy-title border-bottom-0 title-bottom-border">
								<h4>What we <span>Do</span></h4>
							</div>

							<p>The Books-2-Book team comprises of innovative students with a passion for bringing the beauty of IT to our everyday life. Programming can be used not only to develop solutions to problems, but also develops skills such as analysis, creativity, time-management, and so much more. What started out as a hobby, has now become a way of life, as we're constantly pondering ways to use IT to improve daily life, and we wish to develop so much more in future.</p>

						</div>

					</div>

				</div>

